org.apache.taverna.reference.h3

Interface HibernateMappedEntity

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorDocumentImpl, ReferenceSetImpl, T2ReferenceListImpl

    public interface HibernateMappedEntity
    A marker interface used to denote that the component should be registered with the Hibernate ORM system prior to any ExternalReferenceSPI implementations. This is here to allow implementations of e.g. ReferenceSet to be in the implementation package where they belong and still guarantee that they are registered before any other plugins.

    This should be used as an SPI marker, and set as the first SPI registry in the spiRegistries property of the SpiRegistryAwareLocalSessionFactoryBean
